    "description": {
      "value": "<h2 data-start=\"397\" data-end=\"418\">Noble Resilience</h2><p data-start=\"419\" data-end=\"451\"><em data-start=\"419\" data-end=\"451\">11th-level Silver Fang feature</em></p><p data-start=\"453\" data-end=\"511\">You endure hardship through force of will and expectation.</p><p data-start=\"513\" data-end=\"657\">When you <strong data-start=\"522\" data-end=\"545\">fail a saving throw</strong>, you may choose to steel yourself and try again. You can <strong data-start=\"603\" data-end=\"613\">reroll</strong> the saving throw and must use the new roll.</p><p data-start=\"659\" data-end=\"742\">Once you use this feature, you canâ€™t use it again until you finish a <strong data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"741\">long rest</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"744\" data-end=\"866\">If the reroll <strong data-start=\"758\" data-end=\"770\">succeeds</strong>, you gain <strong data-start=\"781\" data-end=\"819\">advantage on the next saving throw</strong> you make before the end of your <strong data-start=\"852\" data-end=\"865\">next turn</strong>.</p>",
